text: Katarina Luketić (born 28 September 1998) is a Croatian volleyball player. She plays as opposite spiker for Italian club Zanetti Bergamo. ==References== ==External links== *Katarina Luketić at CEV.eu Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian women's volleyball players Category:Sportspeople from Zagreb Category:Expatriate volleyball players in Italy
